# NEXO ERP Backend - REST Client Examples
# Install VS Code extension: "REST Client" by Huachao Mao
# Then open this file and click "Send Request" on each request

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3001
@authBaseUrl = http://localhost:3000

### API Gateway Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Auth Service Health Check (Direct)
GET {{authBaseUrl}}/health

### ============================================================================
### AUTHENTICATION ENDPOINTS
### ============================================================================

### Login through API Gateway
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

### Login directly to Auth Service
POST {{authBaseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "admin",
  "password": "password"
}

### Get User Profile (requires JWT token)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/auth/profile
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{}

