### CRM SERVICE ENDPOINTS (Planned)
### ============================================================================

### CRM Health Check
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/crm/health

### Get All Customers
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/crm/customers
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

### Create Customer
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/crm/customers
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{jwt_token}}

{
  "name": "Example Corp",
  "email": "contact@example.com",
  "phone": "+1234567890",
  "address": "123 Main St, City, State 12345"
}

